title: Hobbits
text:
Also called halflings. 
Large hairy feet.
Second breakfast is of critical importance.
Potatoes.

title: Dwarves
text:
Big on mining.
Very strong.
Excellent beards.
Wasted over long distance.

title: Elves
text:
Basically OP in every way.
Snooty.

title: Humans
text:
Win by force of numbers and ability to endure.
Prone to noble sacrifice.
